-- Nestle Nigeria Says That First-Half Profit Through End June Climbs 46%
-- Ana Monteiro
-- 2010-07-30T10:59:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/nestle-nigeria-says-that-first-half-profit-through-end-june-climbs-46-.html

          
          
              Nestle Nigeria Plc, a consumer-
goods maker, said profit in the first half through June surged
46 percent as sales advanced.  
 Net income increased to 6.04 billion naira from 4.15
billion naira a year earlier, the company said in a statement e-
mailed by the Lagos-based Nigerian Stock Exchange today.  
 Revenue gained to 39.2 billion naira from 31.3 billion
naira a year earlier.  
          
          


  


        